series.scope_content: The records consist mostly of loose pages that are in good condition. Some documents are photocopies or carbon copies. There are a few photographs in the records and oversize material such as maps and plans, which have been separated and flattened.
series.arrangement: Arranged alphabetically by subject and chronologically thereunder. Separated materials are arranged similarly.
